  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Kitty or her friends and survive the wave of cat nightmares in this roguelite survivor. The cat automatically throws its toys at enemies; all you have to do is control its path!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/a10aaf75f8ddaf80d283882f5d8fc138.poster.avif?t=1766071489\" width=704 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/a10aaf75f8ddaf80d283882f5d8fc138.webm?t=1766071489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/a10aaf75f8ddaf80d283882f5d8fc138.mp4?t=1766071489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/0650cb168accd3f7c15f6d82eefd2f83.webp?t=1766071489\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, you'll unlock an array of hilarious yet powerful cat-based weaponry that evolves with you. Each weapon starts as a playful toy and transforms into more impressive and dangerous forms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/122ef6bf2a02111f6c114d06cb78e52a.poster.avif?t=1766071489\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/122ef6bf2a02111f6c114d06cb78e52a.webm?t=1766071489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/122ef6bf2a02111f6c114d06cb78e52a.mp4?t=1766071489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/509298fa12c174b9c705eba2e0966698.webp?t=1766071489\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each weapon you acquire is associated with one or more families, each offering distinct bonuses that amplify with every point in it. Will you be a playful cat dropping cute ball, or a nasty one throwing poop at your enemies? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/c2ab2753b8cd3f039909578f4a46e448.poster.avif?t=1766071489\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/c2ab2753b8cd3f039909578f4a46e448.webm?t=1766071489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/c2ab2753b8cd3f039909578f4a46e448.mp4?t=1766071489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/ac9c9601474ff6ee1ddd9abcb7351f5d.webp?t=1766071489\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control one of the different cats, each with its characteristics and starting weapon!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/45e9d7ad89110fe9c78260bfe26bcefd.poster.avif?t=1766071489\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/45e9d7ad89110fe9c78260bfe26bcefd.webm?t=1766071489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/45e9d7ad89110fe9c78260bfe26bcefd.mp4?t=1766071489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/ff05e2b452cd1251c622eea9a1e49883.webp?t=1766071489\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each run, you can purchase permanent upgrades or new cats to play with!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/017fbece7de5961ecde732d1c95ee442.avif?t=1766071489\" width=762 height=440 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/5a8c53826aedddd8d7094aa7d9234937.webp?t=1766071489\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The entire world unfolds within a book created by Kitty's grieving human so she can experience one last adventure. This book contains multiple worlds to explore, each representing a stage of grief.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/7bb70fdfcff5117be0ece40f0033f4a5.webp?t=1766071489\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I am Woum, a one-man army that did everything except the game's sound design! This is my second game on Steam and I really hope you will enjoy this game I made with love 💕</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Kitty or her friends and survive the wave of cat nightmares in this roguelite survivor. The cat automatically throws its toys at enemies; all you have to do is control its path!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/a10aaf75f8ddaf80d283882f5d8fc138.poster.avif?t=1766071489\" width=704 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/a10aaf75f8ddaf80d283882f5d8fc138.webm?t=1766071489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/a10aaf75f8ddaf80d283882f5d8fc138.mp4?t=1766071489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/0650cb168accd3f7c15f6d82eefd2f83.webp?t=1766071489\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, you'll unlock an array of hilarious yet powerful cat-based weaponry that evolves with you. Each weapon starts as a playful toy and transforms into more impressive and dangerous forms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/122ef6bf2a02111f6c114d06cb78e52a.poster.avif?t=1766071489\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/122ef6bf2a02111f6c114d06cb78e52a.webm?t=1766071489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778500/extras/122ef6bf2a02111f