00 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I am Woum, a one-man army that did everything except the game's sound design! This is my second game on Steam and I really hope you will enjoy this game I made with love 💕</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
